## Degradation Matrix

| Pass 1 (Structured) | Pass 2 (Claude subagent) | Pass 3 ({{ adversarial_model }}) | Action |
|---------------------|-------------------------|-------------------------------|--------|
| ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | Full synthesis |
| ✓ | ✓ | ✗ | Synthesis without cross-model, tag `[claude-only]` |
| ✓ | ✗ | ✓ | Synthesis without Claude subagent |
| ✓ | ✗ | ✗ | Single-reviewer mode, note in evaluation |
| ✗ | — | — | FATAL — cannot evaluate. Stop and report error. |
